{"tid":1401606,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同前線講嘅說話","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:16:09.000Z","uid":217413,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4538eca67c468af8001379b22cba5cd23818dfa3","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"首先，我係P牌同埋第一次開po，唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來今日上半場都打得好靚，最後又係搞到大圍捕<br />\n原因都係同一樣：死守<br />\n<br />\n雖然想尊重前線決定，但係一旦你哋被捕，大家要出黎聲援你哋<br />\n而且過咗依個星期，大家都明白到<span style=\"color: red;\">就算只係出黎聲援，班狗照發癲咬人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有人可能會不幸被捕同受傷</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能會有人話咁咪唔好出黎聲援囉，但係你要知道，香港人係好撚善良好撚有義氣，唔會有人選擇放棄你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我希望前線手足明白，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你哋背負嘅唔只係你自己條命，唔該珍惜自己，唔好再送頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外唔排除前線可能有<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">鬼</span></span>，叫大家唔好走，又調返轉頭指責叫人走嘅係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以以後請大家唔好再講&ldquo;唔好走&rdquo;，有人提唔好走嘅話，就要考慮轉場，請大家醒水今個月要試新戰術玩游擊<br />\n大家最擔心嘅都係怕啲人走，少人會危險，咁好簡單，<span style=\"color: red;\">有人唔肯走就拉埋佢走</span><br />\n我哋尊重你哋想守嘅決定，但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你哋要守嘅都要轉場守</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，不割蓆 不分化<br />\nBe water<br />\nHit and run"},{"pid":"1ad23cf75588f80a9557d715acf760d23709718e","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"同埋希望前線唔好灰，大家好嬲都係因為著緊你哋咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc435ee7aa0bedf9d8ac9c35c05759dec2b6d4cb","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"896dd3b87db9eae5cc6463c9fdbb3a177c10e835","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3805ddb9d786fa8b98745c2d6cfc64b2330c7f0","tid":1401606,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"多謝前線<br />\n<br />\n唔好再屌黎屌去 俾意見時注意用詞"},{"pid":"e22a4ca9dc31fa9da2dafd2d6c141d521d36c5bd","tid":1401606,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n你會打返對面就留<br />\n唔係既就唔該走"},{"pid":"709f16be88390749a8640dc38ffdf3814f9be946","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:07:10.000Z","msg":"多謝前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都好愛你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bc560171bce3d7e031cb7a3467a8484b49cad4","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d9a81ffffb950ea710ebf9e787a405c38f5980a","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"大家只係未習慣游擊<br />\n下次再進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfb8395773453ff918d433bab41bb11be9fa0e0","tid":1401606,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"得罪講句下半場同上半場比真係退晒步<br />\n依到無人有心想屌前線<br />\n但都唔好做阿寶次次犯同樣錯誤先得架"},{"pid":"409ccdf329b5d8c52f06c98605b5c9f4351987dd","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"其實上半場做得好好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f596bf0b22e5ed0d2abf0b62b4aeae90d2eb08","tid":1401606,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:16:09.000Z","msg":"[置頂]防暴戰術圖文分析，前線入來睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386199</a>"}]}